PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-1652 (which authorized the AGRICULTURAL STABILIZATION BOARD to make a payment to the CANADIAN SHEEP FEDERATION, for the benefit of wool producers, in order to stabilize the price of wool in 1990), by increasing the total amount that may be paid.
